00:13:45.639 --> 00:13:46.949
joining me.

00:13:46.959 --> 00:13:48.710
You can see the

00:13:48.720 --> 00:13:51.189
squirrels over there;

00:13:51.199 --> 00:13:52.870
they're kind of

00:13:52.880 --> 00:13:55.590
distracting me.

00:13:55.590 --> 00:13:55.600
There

00:13:55.600 --> 00:13:59.430
are

00:13:59.440 --> 00:14:00.910
squirrels everywhere!

00:14:07.440 --> 00:14:09.030
Look at this one

00:14:09.040 --> 00:14:10.590
right next to you.

00:14:19.680 --> 00:14:21.990
They're fat and hungry

00:14:21.990 --> 00:14:22.000
because

00:14:22.000 --> 00:14:25.269
they're eating all these acorns.

00:14:25.279 --> 00:14:28.470
Braden,

00:14:30.030 --> 00:14:30.040
do

00:14:31.790 --> 00:14:31.800
you

00:14:34.120 --> 00:14:36.509
want to

00:14:36.519 --> 00:14:39.389
say hi?

00:14:39.399 --> 00:14:43.949
This is Braden.

00:14:56.959 --> 00:14:58.509
Thank you for

00:14:58.509 --> 00:14:58.519
subscribers, and

00:14:58.519 --> 00:15:00.870
I read your comments

00:15:00.880 --> 00:15:02.710
from all over, like South Korea.

00:15:12.240 --> 00:15:16.310
It's a really pretty

00:15:16.320 --> 00:15:19.030
park; I like the leaves.

00:15:31.959 --> 00:15:36.749
It's going to get cold

00:15:36.759 --> 00:15:39.030
here in

00:15:39.030 --> 00:15:39.040
Tulsa soon.

00:15:39.040 --> 00:15:42.069
I love Tulsa.

00:16:26.040 --> 00:16:28.269
I was on the

00:16:28.279 --> 00:16:29.870
phone with Pastor Steve Cioccolanti for a long

00:16:29.880 --> 00:16:32.030
time today talking about

00:16:40.550 --> 00:16:40.560
Revelation.

00:16:44.720 --> 00:16:48.189
He believes

00:16:48.199 --> 00:16:49.749
we'll go through the war cycle for

00:16:49.749 --> 00:16:49.759
the

00:16:49.759 --> 00:16:53.910
next year or so, and then

00:16:53.920 --> 00:16:56.110
the plague comes. That

00:16:56.120 --> 00:16:57.430
goes with what I've

00:16:57.430 --> 00:16:57.440
seen—a

00:16:57.440 --> 00:16:59.269
massive plague coming during President

00:16:59.279 --> 00:17:01.710
Trump's term.

00:17:01.720 --> 00:17:04.350
If that happens and

00:17:04.360 --> 00:17:06.029
it's part of the green horses, we

00:17:06.039 --> 00:17:08.069
can't stop that. That means

00:17:08.069 --> 00:17:08.079
there

00:17:08.079 --> 00:17:09.870
are

00:17:09.880 --> 00:17:11.150
a lot of people fixing to

00:17:11.150 --> 00:17:11.160
perish.

00:17:11.160 --> 00:17:13.350
That

00:17:13.350 --> 00:17:13.360
is

00:17:13.360 --> 00:17:16.470
terrible, but not for you.

00:17:16.480 --> 00:17:19.150
You're covered in the blood. I saw

00:17:19.160 --> 00:17:21.909
the 'honey glow'on the

00:17:21.909 --> 00:17:21.919
body of Christ.

00:17:21.919 --> 00:17:23.789
I saw people in makeshift military tents with

00:17:23.789 --> 00:17:23.799
the glory of the Lord resting

00:17:23.799 --> 00:17:25.710
on

00:17:25.710 --> 00:17:25.720
them,

00:17:25.720 --> 00:17:29.350
laying hands on people

00:17:33.360 --> 00:17:34.669
and

00:17:38.600 --> 00:17:41.270
seeing

00:17:46.039 --> 00:17:47.390
them

00:17:47.400 --> 00:17:50.029
get

00:17:50.039 --> 00:17:51.750
up

00:17:51.760 --> 00:17:53.630
because the power of God was resting on

00:17:57.400 --> 00:17:59.590
them.

00:18:01.840 --> 00:18:03.990
We have

00:18:04.000 --> 00:18:05.710
that same authority.

00:18:11.039 --> 00:18:13.070
If that

00:18:13.080 --> 00:18:14.710
green horse is riding in

00:18:14.710 --> 00:18:14.720
2026,

00:18:14.720 --> 00:18:17.430
it's

00:18:17.430 --> 00:18:17.440
interesting

00:18:17.440 --> 00:18:20.350
because

00:18:20.360 --> 00:18:23.590
it

00:18:23.590 --> 00:18:23.600
puts

00:18:23.600 --> 00:18:26.470
a time frame on my visions.

00:18:26.480 --> 00:18:27.750
I'm

00:18:27.760 --> 00:18:31.750
just

00:18:34.520 --> 00:18:36.789
turning that around in my noggin.

00:18:39.799 --> 00:18:43.510
Anyway,

00:18:48.440 --> 00:18:49.909
let's

00:18:49.919 --> 00:18:51.070
look at these squirrels.

00:18:51.080 --> 00:18:53.950
They're

00:18:53.960 --> 00:18:57.710
bold!

00:18:57.720 --> 00:19:01.310
Look at that big plump one right

00:19:01.320 --> 00:19:03.669
there.

00:19:30.440 --> 00:19:33.070
My grandpa would say that's

00:19:33.080 --> 00:19:36.470
stew. We'd sit out

00:19:36.480 --> 00:19:38.430
for hours

00:19:38.440 --> 00:19:40.149
so grandma could fry those up, but they

00:19:40.149 --> 00:19:40.159
tasted

00:19:40.159 --> 00:19:42.950
so rough and nasty. I'd

00:19:42.950 --> 00:19:42.960
ask

00:19:42.960 --> 00:19:44.510
why we were eating

00:19:45.470 --> 00:19:45.480
rodents,

00:19:48.400 --> 00:19:51.190
but that's what we did as

00:19:51.200 --> 00:19:53.390
kids.

00:19:56.760 --> 00:20:01.029
It was gross.

00:20:01.039 --> 00:20:04.870
I'm

00:20:06.909 --> 00:20:06.919
just

00:20:08.360 --> 00:20:10.270
thinking

00:20:10.280 --> 00:20:12.549
about childhood

00:20:12.549 --> 00:20:12.559
stuff—squirrels

00:20:12.559 --> 00:20:15.549
and

00:20:15.559 --> 00:20:17.710
rabbits.

00:20:20.840 --> 00:20:26.190
Look at

00:20:26.200 --> 00:20:29.110
those

00:20:35.919 --> 00:20:38.350
geese.

00:20:48.280 --> 00:20:51.630
Big old

00:20:51.640 --> 00:20:54.650
Canadians!

00:21:17.799 --> 00:21:20.070
Look at

00:21:20.070 --> 00:21:20.080
that

00:21:20.080 --> 00:21:22.669
massive

00:21:22.669 --> 00:21:22.679
oak

00:21:22.679 --> 00:21:26.750
tree; it

00:21:26.750 --> 00:21:26.760
must be

00:21:26.760 --> 00:21:30.390
several hundred years old.

00:22:03.760 --> 00:22:06.909
I hope you enjoy these prayer

00:22:06.919 --> 00:22:08.190
videos. I try to

00:22:08.190 --> 00:22:08.200
do

00:22:08.200 --> 00:22:09.350
something different so you

00:22:09.360 --> 00:22:11.590
don't get bored.

00:22:20.679 --> 00:22:23.230
My job in this

00:22:23.230 --> 00:22:23.240
end-time

00:22:23.240 --> 00:22:25.669
ministry is to bring in as

00:22:25.679 --> 00:22:28.070
many souls as I can and tell you that

00:22:28.080 --> 00:22:30.230
Jesus is a healer.

00:22:37.350 --> 00:22:37.360
Nothing

00:22:44.679 --> 00:22:46.029
else

00:22:46.039 --> 00:22:49.029
matters other than the Great

00:22:49.039 --> 00:22:51.110
Commission.

00:22:51.120 --> 00:22:53.669
If

00:22:53.679 --> 00:22:55.990
Jesus is

00:22:55.990 --> 00:22:56.000
giving

00:22:56.000 --> 00:22:58.510
us a four-year

00:22:58.520 --> 00:23:01.549
window of reprieve in America,

00:23:01.559 --> 00:23:03.669
let's

00:23:03.679 --> 00:23:07.029
do all we can so that

00:23:07.039 --> 00:23:09.149
not one should perish.

00:23:19.279 --> 00:23:22.590
Jesus is coming soon. I

00:23:22.600 --> 00:23:24.990
believe at the end of the next shmita cycle, we'll

00:23:25.000 --> 00:23:27.630
see... that's just my

00:23:27.640 --> 00:23:29.029
opinion

00:23:29.039 --> 00:23:31.269
based

00:23:31.279 --> 00:23:32.510
on

00:23:32.520 --> 00:23:34.430
what

00:23:36.919 --> 00:23:38.630
Billy Brim and Rick Renner

00:23:38.630 --> 00:23:38.640
and others

00:23:38.640 --> 00:23:40.630
teach. You

00:23:40.630 --> 00:23:40.640
pick the

00:23:40.640 --> 00:23:42.990
Bible scholars

00:23:43.000 --> 00:23:44.950
you stand

00:23:44.960 --> 00:23:47.549
by.

00:23:47.559 --> 00:23:49.950
Thank

00:23:49.960 --> 00:23:51.909
you for joining me today. Look at

00:23:53.799 --> 00:23:56.669
those

00:23:56.679 --> 00:24:00.070
massive dogs!

00:24:11.200 --> 00:24:14.390
Like, subscribe, and we'll see

00:24:14.400 --> 00:24:16.390
you tomorrow. Put a smile

00:24:16.400 --> 00:24:18.350
on your face and a song in your heart.

00:24:18.360 --> 00:24:20.350
Jesus loves you.

00:24:20.360 --> 00:24:22.149
God bless you and have a wonderful

00:24:22.159 --> 00:24:25.600
day. Bye-bye.

